Apache AMQP based network logger.

Put the following in your apache config:


CustomLog "|/usr/local/logspray/bin/logspray.rb --host=myamqploghost --queue=apache_access_log" combined
ErrorLog "|/usr/local/logspray/bin/logspray.rb --host=myamqploghost --queue=apache_error_log"


add this cronjob on your log server:


* * * * *       ruby /usr/local/logspray/bin/consume_logspray_queue.rb --host=myamqploghost --queue=apache_access_log
* * * * *       ruby /usr/local/logspray/bin/consume_logspray_queue.rb --host=myamqploghost --queue=apache_error_log
